---
import GlitchText from './GlitchText.astro';
---
<section class="hero relative min-h-screen flex flex-col justify-between overflow-hidden bg-ink scanlines">
  <header class="relative z-10 flex items-center justify-between p-6 md:p-10 font-mono text-xs md:text-sm uppercase tracking-wider text-parchment/70">
    <span>Port Arthur · TX</span>
    <span class="hidden md:inline">Unofficial Fan Archive · v1.0</span>
    <span>1987 — ∞</span>
  </header>

  <div class="relative z-10 flex-1 flex flex-col justify-center items-center text-center px-4">
    <div class="font-display text-mega leading-[0.8] text-parchment select-none">
      <GlitchText text="UGK" class="block" />
    </div>

    <h1 class="mt-2 md:mt-6 font-heading text-huge leading-none uppercase tracking-brutal text-gold max-w-5xl">
      Короли с Юга
    </h1>

    <p class="mt-6 md:mt-8 max-w-2xl text-base md:text-xl font-body text-parchment/80">
      Pimp C · Bun B · Port Arthur, Техас.
      Дуэт, который сформировал язык южного хип-хопа и оставил каталог,
      от которого никто не отходит тридцать лет.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-8 md:mt-12 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 items-center justify-center">
      <a
        href="#essential-tracks"
        class="group brutal-border inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-gold text-ink px-8 py-4 font-heading text-xl uppercase tracking-wider hover:bg-crimson hover:text-parchment transition-colors"
      >
        Слушать эссеншиалы
        <span aria-hidden="true" class="group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform">→</span>
      </a>
      <a
        href="https://www.discogs.com/artist/32130-UGK"
        rel="nofollow noopener"
        target="_blank"
        class="brutal-border-crimson inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-ink text-parchment px-8 py-4 font-heading text-xl uppercase tracking-wider hover:bg-crimson transition-colors"
      >
        Винил на Discogs ↗
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="relative z-10 grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-px bg-parchment/20 border-t border-parchment/20 font-mono text-xs md:text-sm">
    <div class="bg-ink p-4 md:p-6">
      <div class="text-parchment/50">АЛЬБОМОВ</div>
      <div class="text-gold text-2xl md:text-4xl font-heading mt-1">06</div>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-ink p-4 md:p-6">
      <div class="text-parchment/50">ЛЕТ ВМЕСТЕ</div>
      <div class="text-gold text-2xl md:text-4xl font-heading mt-1">20+</div>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-ink p-4 md:p-6">
      <div class="text-parchment/50">BILLBOARD</div>
      <div class="text-gold text-2xl md:text-4xl font-heading mt-1">#1</div>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-ink p-4 md:p-6">
      <div class="text-parchment/50">PLATINUM</div>
      <div class="text-gold text-2xl md:text-4xl font-heading mt-1">01</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
